      "date": "2018-12-14 09:49:40.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThis issue was not seen before is because client readdir specified LUDA_TYPE, and lu_dirent_calc_size() aligned if it's set, which happened to avoid this issue, but mdd_dir_is_empty() doesn't set LUDA_TYPE, so the record packed only contains lu_dirent, name and '\\0', but its size doesn't include the pending '\\0', which caused crash in building page.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
